---
description: XHSSpec workflow rule
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

Use this repo's `.xhsspec/` directory as the source of truth for Xiaohongshu operations.

- Read `.xhsspec/config.yaml`, `brand/*`, `strategy/*`, and `specs/*` before drafting.
- Keep long-lived knowledge in repo files, not in ad hoc chat memory.
- Use `xhs-spec quick`, `xhs-spec hot`, `xhs-spec plan`, `xhs-spec review`, and `xhs-spec archive` for deterministic workflow steps.
- Use `xhs-spec publish` to generate screenshot-ready publish artifacts from a finished draft.
- When the user asks to write a post quickly, route to the quick workflow.
- When the user asks about a trend or whether to react to one, route to the trend workflow.
- When the user asks for a structured series or campaign, route to the campaign workflow.
- Use `<placeholder>...</placeholder>` for intentionally incomplete fields instead of vague filler text.
